Help on spell:   Spell that increases the increase of hp
Casting time:    6 rounds
Spell cost:      276 SPs
Spell type:      heal
Spell words:     consuming spell points to increase the rate at which hit points
                 periodically increase
Affecting stats: wisdom, intelligence, flow of life and mastery of medicine

It is a known fact that hit points will periodically increase over time,
until reaching a certain integer defined as the hit point maximum. The rate
at which hit points increase in this periodic manner can itself be increased,
including by use of magical incantations such as the 'spell that increases
the increase of hp'. Unfortunately, while this spell increases the rate at
which hit points automatically increase, it also decreases the amount of
spell points held by the caster.
