Help on spell: Spell that reduces reduction of hp
Casting time:  7 rounds
Spell cost:    212 SPs
Spell type:    defensive
Spell words:   i will cast a spell on you that reduces the damage you take

The 'spell that reduces reduction of hp' is a magical technique
that works by taking the amount of hp by which the target's hit points
will be reduced, and reducing that amount, thereby reducing the reduction
to the players hp, and leaving more hp behind on the player for future
reducing. The spell also reduces some sp from the caster of the 'spell that
reduces reduction of hp', in exchange for reducing the redution of
hp for the target.
