Help on spell:   Spell that reduces sp and reduces hp
Casting time:    3 rounds
Spell cost:      329 SPs
Spell type:      attack
Damage type:     death
Spell damage:    340 - 420
Spell words:     consuming spell points to decrement victim's hit points
Affecting stats: intelligence, wisdom and spell percent

The spell known as 'spell that reduces sp and reduces hp' is a magical
incantation that subtracts spell points from the caster, resulting in
the subtraction of a usually larger number of hit points from the
target. After subtracting enough hit points from a target, the caster
can receive various forms of virtual currency which are subsequently
used to increase the caster's power, so that the caster may cast more
spells that reduce the caster's spell points and reduce the victim's hit
points.